reviewText:
OK
Wanted more scenery and less travel tips.
Having visited some of these places...wanted to refresh memories.
Let me know when the DVD's are on sale.

We bought this book for  rip 15 years ago.  I proved to be invaluable during our entire three weeks in Germany, Ausria, Italy, Switzerland and Holland and then me alone in Sweden and Norway another week.  Stan Sattelberg in Salt Lake City.
